summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Alley in Block Forty-nine Yesler Second Addition Supp. Central in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 21210, creating Local Improvement District No. 2116 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
